{"tid":1177077,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"指原莉乃封咪　為11年偶像生涯劃上句號","createTime":"2019-05-29T14:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T15:08:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"819339cd59d39b046788d5168070283478be32e4","tid":1177077,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190529215007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190529215007&h=fa2b24a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190529215007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190529215007&h=932dbafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶領HKT48師妹演出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190529215007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190529215007&h=cb3313d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向粉絲力薦師妹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_10p.jpg?20190529215007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529210214662-0529_00862_001_10p.jpg%3F20190529215007&h=de85d18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後將無線咪放入櫃桶，象徵正式封咪。<br />\n<br />\n日本女團HKT48一姐指原莉乃4月28日在橫濱舉行畢業演唱會後，為了答謝家鄉福岡的粉絲11年來支持，昨日在福岡海洋會展中心舉行《指原莉乃大感謝祭》，並作現場直播。<br />\n<br />\n當晚吸引8,000名歌迷捧場，指原莉乃演唱多首代表作，包括投考AKB48時唱的《BIMGO！》，她又帶領HKT48師妹演出，向粉絲力薦師妹。她演唱第一首歌已開始眼濕濕，期間不時感觸落淚，演唱完最後一首歌後，她向粉絲大喊：「11年來，感謝大家。」然後將無線咪放入櫃桶，象徵封咪跟粉絲正式道別，為11年的偶像生涯寫上句號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697363778687f4d66292a15259101ce12c71b9e8","tid":1177077,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:01:10.000Z","msg":"牙醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c0f1d6d908c2f1b4a3b15a33002d94719b3600","tid":1177077,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"40baff4c9d351ec637aef64913cab24de6b14697","tid":1177077,"uid":251836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"正式收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2f39581494879b36aaea7d8c219df7b01a8139","tid":1177077,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c0f1d6d908c2f1b4a3b15a33002d94719b3600","tid":1177077,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-